0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4122:\"\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/wp-57.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"644\" height=\"443\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/wp-57.png\" alt=\"Phin bn WordPress 5.7\" class=\"wp-image-974\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/wp-57.png 644w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/wp-57-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Phin bn WordPress 5.7 mang li nhng ci tin v giao din trong qun tr, cp nht phin bn jQuery v  cung cp mt s tnh nng mi. Hy cng team WordPress im danh nhng chc nng c nhc n.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-971\"></span>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/about-57-cover.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"632\" height=\"326\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/about-57-cover.jpg\" alt=\"Giao din trnh son tho\" class=\"wp-image-973\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/about-57-cover.jpg 632w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2021/03/about-57-cover-300x155.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 632px) 100vw, 632px\" /></a><figcaption>Giao din trnh son tho</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trnh son tho khi &#8211; Block Editor</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>iu chnh font ch  bt k u vi cc i tng l ch</li><li>Ci tin khi ti s dng tt hn, bao gm t ng lu khi click nt Cp nht</li><li>Chn khi bng cch ko r t ct bn vo khung son tho.</li><li>Cc khi c thm chc nng chiu cao bng mn hnh (full-height)</li><li>Khi button &#8211; nt bm &#8211; cho php chn cn i theo chiu dc hay ngang</li><li>Khi icon mng x hi nay c th chn kch thc icon</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trang Qun tr admin</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Giao din qun tr c cp nht tng mu vi  ph sng tt hn, p ng tiu chun WCAG 2.0 v t l tng phn.</li><li>Chuyn i kt ni t HTTP sang HTTPS d dng vi 1 c click. Tnh nng ny bao gm c chc nng cp nht database  m bo cc lin kt trong web khng b die.</li><li>Cp nht giao din ng nhp v ng k.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cp nht khc</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Cp nht Robots API: Thm thuc tnh <code>max-image-preview: large</code> mc nh.</li><li>Gn tag <code>loading=\"lazy\"</code> cho tt c iframe nu c thuc tnh <code>width</code> v <code>height</code> sn c.</li><li>Cp nht phin bn jQuery 3.5.1 (iu ny c th gy ra mt s li khng tng thch trn cc phin bn giao din v plugin, bao gm c Bootstrap jQuery, nu bn gp li nh vy, hy lin h vi tc gi ca plugin hoc giao din).</li><li>Cp nht thm ti liu v Field cho Block Editor.</li><li>Thm function mi  kim tra bi vit  trng thi cng khai:<code> is_post_status_viewable</code></li><li>Cho php Post (bi vit) c th chn quan h cha con vi bi vit khc.</li><li>Nng cp Crons API  x l li tt hn.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bn dch ting Vit</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>[DONE] Bn dch giao din bn ngoi (Frontend)  hon tt cho phin bn WordPress 5.7.</li><li>Bn dch trang qun tr cn 136 words cha c dch, rt mong nhn c s ng gp ca mi ngi.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngi son v dch s lc bn cp nht:<br>Nguyn Minh Khi (Founder &#8211; <a href=\"https://codetot.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">CODE TT</a>)<br><em>Locale Manager @ team WordPress ting Vit</em></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2021/03/16/phien-ban-wordpress-5-7-esperanza/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_exp