i nghim phin bn Windows bn quyn trn vn m khng lo mt ph. Win 11 vi nhng ci tin v giao din v c nng cao bo mt, gip ti u c hiu sut cng vic ca ngi dng.\r\n<h4><strong>Trang b cm bin vn tay, Pin 2 cell 37Wh</strong></h4>\r\nLaptop Asus X515EA-BQ2351W c trang b cm bin vn tay tch hp ngay trong touchpad ca my tnh cho php ngi dng ch mt ng mt c chm  mi th c sn sng. Vic bo mt bng vn tay c th gip bo mt laptop ca mnh tt hn, m app hay thanh ton online c thun tin hn.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_9d625d6b-04b5-4a85-9ab7-d8bcdcc7b549.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Dung lng pin cao\" /></figure>\r\nAsus  trang b cho chic laptop ny mt vin pin lin 2 cell 37Wh , cho php ngi dng mt thi lng va   c th tri nghim gii tr hay lm vic m khng phi qu lo lng v vic chic laptop ca mnh s ht pin gia chng.\r\n<h4><strong>Mua laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W ti Phong V c min ph giao hng| H tr bo hnh 24 thng</strong></h4>\r\nVivobook X515EA-BQ2351W c mc gi u i ti cc<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/phongvu.vn/contact\"><strong>showroom Phong V</strong></a>. Ngoi ra, nu khng th n cc ca hng ca Phong V th bn s c chng ti min ph giao hng tn nh. Sn phm cn c Phong V cam kt 100% hng chnh hng v h tr bo hnh ln n 24 thng.', 'Laptop ASUS Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W (i3-1115G4/RAM 4GB/512GB SSD/ Windows 11)', '- CPU: Intel Core i3-1115G4\r\n- Mn hnh: 15.6\" IPS (1920 x 1080)\r\n- RAM: 1 x 4GB Onboard DDR4\r\n-  ha: Onboard Intel UHD Graphics\r\n- Lu tr: 512GB SSD M.2 NVMe /\r\n- H iu hnh: Windows 11 Home\r\n- Pin: 2 cell 37 Wh\r\n- Khi lng: 1.8kg', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'laptop-asus-vivobook-x515ea-bq2351w-i3-1115g4-ram-4gb-512gb-ssd-windows-11', '', '', '2023-04-23 17:34:20', '2023-04-24 00:34:20', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=15', 0, 'product', '', 0),
