(85, 1, '2023-03-30 00:13:10', '2023-03-30 07:13:10', '<h3><a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/c/laptop\"><strong>Laptop</strong></a><strong>Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W l mt trong nhng dng laptop c nhiu sinh vin a chung. Vi gi thnh khng qu cao, chic laptop ny nhanh chng c sn n vi thit k hin i v hiu nng n nh, cho bn mt tri nghim th v.</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Kiu dng thanh lch, nh gn d dng mang theo</strong></h4>\r\nLaptop Asus Vivobook c v ngoi v cng bt mt vi kiu dng gn nh, thanh lch, mn hnh c thit k vin siu mng v mu xm tot ln v mnh m v hin i. Phn vin mn hnh vn l mt mu en quen thuc v logo ASUS to im nhn.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_051dfd2e-8a66-4630-9728-952529e41383.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Thit k gn gng\" /></figure>\r\nn tng hn na khi m chic ASUS VivoBook X515EA ny c kch thc 36 x 23.5 x 1.99 cm cng trng lng ch 1.8kg, rt nh d y ch l mt chic laptop 15,6 inch. Pha trn mn hnh cng c trang b mt chic VGA webcam tin li cho vic hc trc tuyn, hp online ca ngi dng.\r\n<h4><strong>Mn hnh 15,6 inch Full HD sc nt, trang b tm nn IPS</strong></h4>\r\nLaptop Asus X515EA-BQ2351W c trang b mn hnh 15.6 inch c  phn gii l 1920 x 1080 pixels (Full HD). Tm nn IPS ca chic my tnh ny cng cho kh nng hin th hnh nh c sc nt hn nhng mn hnh thng vi di mu rng, gim c nh sng xanh, tng cng cc chi tit trong mi iu kin nh sng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_86e4d140-54d8-4fd6-b5b9-02def6aee434.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Mn hnh 15.6 inch\" /></figure>\r\nThm vo , em laptop ny cng s hu mn hnh chng la gip mn hnh khng b chi sng, b bng gng k c trong cc iu kin nh sng gt. Cng vi , mn hnh ny cng gip ngi dng trnh mi mt khi s dng trong mt thi gian di, ph hp vi dn vn phng hay sinh vin phi dng my thng xuyn.\r\n<h4><strong>Hiu nng n nh, Intel Core i3-1115G4 cho mi tc v mt m</strong></h4>\r\