(119, 1, '2023-03-30 01:42:04', '2023-03-30 08:42:04', '<h2>B 4 phin bn iPhone 12 vn ang cn c sc ht cha ngui i, th Apple li mang n cho ngi dng mt siu phm mi<a href=\"http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/danh-muc-san-pham/san_pham_apple/iphone_ipad/\">iPhone 13</a>vi nhiu ci tin th v ha hn s mang li nhng tri nghim hp dn nht cho ngi s dng.</h2>\r\n<h3>Thit k sang trng, ng cp hn v ngoi hnh</h3>\r\nin thoi iPhone 13 c thit k nguyn khi vung vn nh phin bn tin nhim, khung vin c lm t nhm, nt p sang trng vi mt lng knh cao cp. Ngoi hnh khng khc bit lm so vi tin nhim, nhng t l mn hnh vi khung my tt hn.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_81a30583-e04f-4257-a4c8-30307980b31d.jpeg\" alt=\"Thit k sang trng\" /></figure>\r\nPhn tai th ca phin bn 13 ny nh hn khong 20%  tng din tch tri nghim khi lt web, xem phim hay chi game. Khi lng my 174g,  dy ch 0.765 cm.\r\n\r\nim khc bit ln nht trn ngoi hnh gip to im nhn din c trng, mi m v p mt, sang chnh hn c l chnh l cc cm bin camera c t cho thay v xp thng hng nh iPhone 12. Mu\r\n\r\nMidnight sang trng, iPhone 13 chng nhn chun khng nc v bi IP68 yn tm s dng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_2a5bf057-c702-43b8-877d-924895ebe526.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Thit k sang trng ng cp\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Mn hnh Super Retina XDR tuyt ho,  sng cao, tit kim pin</h3>\r\niPhone 13 vi kch thc mn hnh 6.1 inch, s dng tm nn OLED cho cht lng mu sc sng ng v chi tit hnh nh sc nt,  phn gii ln n 2532 x 1170 px. Lp oleophobic c ph pha ngoi mn hnh gip hn ch tnh trng bm bi bn v m hi tay ca ngi dng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_058d0488-10e7-4a61-841d-da0baa3f0076.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Mn hnh retina mnh m\" /></figure>\r\nCng ngh mn hnh Super Retina XDR nh cao gip t  sng 800 nits, ti a ln n 1200 nits, di mu rng P3, n nh tt mu sc v cht lng hin th nh trong nhng iu kin chiu sng thp hay mi trng nng gay gt, nh sng chi vi t l tng phn ln.\r\n<h3>Hiu nng mnh m nh chip Apple A15 Bionic</h3>\r\niPhone 13 c hiu nng cc k n tng vi trang b con chip Apple A15 Bionic siu mnh c sn xut trn quy trnh 5 nm, hiu nng CPU nhanh hn khong 50%, GPU nhanh hn khong 30% so vi cc i th trong cng phn khc.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_a15d87e6-3270-4f7e-8738-ba2726157b2b.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Hiu nng mnh m\" /></figure>\r\nHiu nng ci tin hn  ngi dng c c nhng tri nghim tt hn trn in thoi khi dng cc ng dng gii tr, chnh sa nh, video hay c th chin cc ta game c  ha cao vi s n nh v mt m nht c th. in thoi iPhone 13 trang b b nh trong 128 GB l tng  tha thc lu tr.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_4ef7237b-e269-4c7c-9538-c27486dece1e.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | B nh trong 128gb\" /></figure>\r\nChun mng di ng 5G c ci thin cht lng vi bng tn vt tri, vi 5G gip in thoi c th xem trc tuyn hay ti xung nhanh chng. Khng dng  , siu phm ny c ch  d liu thng minh, t ng pht hin, gim ti tc  mng nhm gip tit kim nng lng khi khng cn dng tc  cao.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_12205a2b-fa99-4099-8ab8-fd218ea29119.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Hiu nng mnh m\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>nh cao in nh vi cm camera kp ni bt</h3>\r\niPhone 13 trang b cm camera kp pha sau s hu  phn gii 12 MP, cht lng nh chp c ci thin hn so vi phin bn tin nhim vi kh nng thu sng ca camera chnh ln n 47%. Camera vi gc chp siu rng cho gc nhn 120   thu c nhiu chi tit hn, d dng ghi li nhng k nim ni non hng v hay nh chp nhm ng ngi.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_e7717644-2e00-460d-ba83-f11278134a50.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Chp nh nh cao\" /></figure>\r\nTnh nng chng rung quang hc Sensor Shift cng c trang b vo phin bn 13 ny gip ly nt nhanh chng, kh nng chp m tr nn r nt m t b nhiu ht, ch  quay video cng rt n nh v mt m hn. Camera trc vn c nm trong tai th,  phn gii cng t 12 MP vi cc cng ngh chp nh mi nht nh hiu ng bokeh, ch  in nh, Memoji v Animoji.\r\n<h3>Thi lng s dng c ci thin - Cng ngh sc ci tin</h3>\r\nTheo cng b ca Apple, phin bn 13 ny c thi lng pin tng thm khong 2.5 ting so vi tin nhim, cho thi gian s dng lu hn nhm phc v hiu quhn cho ngi dng c nhu cu s dng vi tn sut cao.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/6/16/20220616_d8d4299e-c4de-45cb-a913-4b73324bc15d.jpeg\" alt=\"iPhone 13 128GB Midnight | Ti u ha nng lng\" /></figure>\r\nH tr sc nhanh 20 W c kh nng np y 50% pin ch trong vng 30 pht. Cng ngh pin lithium , cng ngh sc khng dy tin tin MagSafe v Qi. Cng sc Lightning, loi sim Nano SIM v eSIM cht lng. Jack tai nghe loi Lightning. Kt ni wifi hiu qu WiFi 6 (802.11ax) vi MIMO. Kt ni GPS hin i GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, QZSS, BeiDou.\r\n\r\nXem thm:<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/iphone-13-pro-max--p418544\">iPhone 13 Pro max</a>,<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/iphone-14--p459613\">iPhone 14</a>\r\n<h3>Mua in Thoi Di ng iPhone 13 128GB Midnight chnh hng| Phong V bo hnh ln n 12 thng</h3>\r\niPhone 13 em n s ng cp cho bt c c nhn no s hu, ng thi tri nghim nh cao tuyt vi khi s dng mt chic in thoi thng minh. Mua in thoi iPhone ti Phong V  nhn c s an tm s dng vi cht lng chnh hng, chnh sch bo hnh tuyt vi cng u i mua sm hp dn.', 'iPhone 13 | Chnh Hng VNA', '- Chnh hng, Mi 100%, Nguyn seal\r\n- Mn hnh: 6.1\" - Super Retina XDR OLED\r\n- Camera sau: 2x 12MP\r\n- Camera trc: 12MP\r\n- CPU: Apple A15 Bionic\r\n- B nh: 256GB\r\n- H iu hnh: IOS', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'iphone-13-chinh-hang-vna', '', '', '2023-05-27 07:15:37', '2023-05-27 14:15: