(286, 1, '2023-04-23 19:15:30', '2023-04-24 02:15:30', '<h2>HeadphonesLogitech H150 (White)many modern technologies at a reasonable price</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trng) | gi thnh hp l\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Overview of the Logitech H150 . Headset</h3>\r\n<h3>ENJOY HOURS OF INTERNET CALLS AND LISTEN TO MUSIC FROM COMPUTER WITH CLEAR, CLEAN SOUND.</h3>\r\nFlexible and adjustable, for computers that use separate 3.5mm audio and microphone jacks. In-line controls let you adjust the volume or mute calls without interrupting. Noise canceling microphone reduces background noise.\r\n<h3>main function</h3>\r\n(Pictures of the same type and color are for illustrative purposes of the product)\r\n\r\n1. STRUCTURE\r\n\r\nFull stereo sound delivers crystal clear, clear quality for voice, video calls, music, games and more. Stereo headphones for both personal use or in the office.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng1.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trng) | M THANH NI\" /></figure>\r\n2. Swivel MICRO\r\n\r\nThe mic boom can be rotated 180 to be worn on the left or right side. The flexible mic can be conveniently positioned for better voice capture and background noise reduction. The mic boom folds inside the strap for a neat look when you\'re not using it.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng2.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logitech H150 (Trng) | MICR XOAY\" /></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"image\">\r\n3. ONLINE CONTROL BUTTON\r\n\r\nConveniently located controls on the headset cord allow you to adjust the volume or mute calls without interruption.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Tai-nghe-Logitech-H150-Tr%E1%BA%AFng3-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Logi