(305, 1, '2023-04-23 20:04:58', '2023-04-24 03:04:58', '<h3><a href=\"http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/danh-muc-san-pham/lap_top/\"><strong>Laptop</strong></a>Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W is one of the most popular laptops among students. At a low price, this laptop is quickly sought after with its modern design and stable performance, giving you an enjoyable experience.</h3>\r\n<h4>Elegant design, compact and easy to carry</h4>\r\nAsus Vivobook laptop has an extremely eye-catching appearance with a compact, elegant design, an ultra-thin bezel design and gray color that exudes a strong and modern look. The screen border is still a familiar black color and the ASUS logo creates a highlight.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_051dfd2e-8a66-4630-9728-952529e41383.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Thit k gn gng\" /></figure>\r\nEven more impressive when this ASUS VivoBook X515EA has dimensions of 36 x 23.5 x 1.99 cm and a weight of only 1.8kg, very light even though this is only a 15.6-inch laptop. Above the screen is also equipped with a convenient VGA webcam for users\' online learning and online meetings.\r\n<h4>15.6-inch Full HD screen sharp, equipped with IPS panels</h4>\r\nAsus X515EA-BQ2351W laptop is equipped with a 15.6-inch screen with a resolution of 1920 x 1080 pixels (Full HD). The IPS panel of this computer also gives the ability to display images that are sharper than regular screens with a wide color range, reducing blue light, enhancing details in all lighting conditions.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_86e4d140-54d8-4fd6-b5b9-02def6aee434.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Mn hnh 15.6 inch\" /></figure>\r\nIn addition, this laptop also has an anti-glare screen that prevents the screen from being bright, mirrored even in harsh lighting conditions. Along with that, this screen also helps users avoid eye strain when used for a long time, suitable for office workers or students who have to use the device frequently.\r\n<h4>Stable performance, Intel Core i3-1115G4 for all smooth tasks</h4>\r\nAsus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W has an ideal configuration for office work when the power of the machine not only comes from Intel core i3-1115G4 processor (3.0 GHz - 4.10 GHz / 6MB / 2 cores, 4 threads) but and from 1 x 4GB Onboard DDR4 RAM (1 slot) for high performance.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_51218c7d-8fcf-4db8-91ce-e2ea2d0ac8ae.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Hiu nng mnh m\" /></figure>\r\nThis chip saves battery when manufactured on the advanced 10nm SuperFin process. Meanwhile, 4GB DDR4 RAM on board also helps users operate the machine more smoothly and smoothly.\r\n<h4>Equipped with Intel UHD Graphics and  512GB SSD hard drive</h4>\r\nIn addition, Vivobook X515EA owns an Intel UHD Graphics chip that also helps you to perform basic office tasks, or browse the web, entertainment, watching movies, basic office more smoothly.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_7289ad5f-a4ac-4e24-8cb7-a2b2a504e9e1.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Dung lng lu tr cao\" /></figure>\r\nIn addition, this Asus Vivobook laptop also has a 512GB SSD M.2 NVMe hard drive available, both for large storage capacity and able to comprehensively speed up the computer. This hard drive combines with the machine\'s RAM memory, giving you a space just enough for storing documents, photos, and videos easily.\r\n<h4>Full connection support, Windows 11 Home operating system</h4>\r\nThe Asus laptop also fully supports common connections such as: 1 USB 3.2 Type C port, 1 USB 3.2 port, 2 USB 2.0 ports, 1 HDMI port. Thanks to the full range of ports on this computer, you can connect to all peripheral devices to optimize your work.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_6839c0d9-2a49-4df6-8809-2008858215ac.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | a dng cng kt ni\" /></figure>\r\nASUS has equipped the Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W laptop with Windows 11 Home operating system, allowing you to experience the full copyrighted version of Windows without worrying about costs. Win 11 with interface improvements and enhanced security, helps optimize the user\'s work performance.\r\n<h4>Equipped with fingerprint sensor, 2-cell battery 37Wh</h4>\r\nAsus X515EA-BQ2351W laptop is equipped with a fingerprint sensor integrated in the computer\'s touchpad allowing users to only take one touch to have everything ready. Fingerprint security can help secure your laptop better, open apps or pay online more conveniently.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_9d625d6b-04b5-4a85-9ab7-d8bcdcc7b549.jpg\" alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Dung lng pin cao\" /></figure>\r\nAsus has equipped this laptop with a 2-cell 37Wh battery, allowing users a sufficient amount of time to be able to experience entertainment or work without having to worry about their laptop running out of battery. in the middle.\r\n<h4>Buy Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W laptop in Phong Vu and get free shipping | Warranty support 24 months</h4>\r\nVivobook X515EA-BQ2351W has a preferential price at Phong Vu showrooms. In addition, if you cannot go to Phong Vu\'s stores, we will provide free home delivery. Products are also guaranteed by Phong Vu 100% genuine and support warranty up to 24 months.', 'Laptop ASUS Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W (i3-1115G4/RAM 4GB/512GB SSD/ Windows 11)', '- CPU: Intel Core i3-1115G4\r\n- Screen: 15.6\" IPS (1920 x 1080)\r\n- RAM: 1 x 4GB Onboard DDR4\r\n- Graphics: Onboard Intel UHD