e afternoon and then watch movies in the evening, with durable battery life that will be a great assistant for users.\r\n<h2>Take sharp photos and videos</h2>\r\nThe front camera of Ipad Gen 9thth 2021 is greatly upgraded with a resolution of up to 12MP and a super-wide angle that increases clear image quality, taking impressive selfies even when shooting a group, a large group of people. In particular, during video calls, the Ipad Gen 9th 2021 central stage mode can automatically adjust so that you are always in the middle of the frame and is very useful when studying and meeting online.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_59de790c-4cb3-401d-9364-e2991a13f02a.jpg\" alt=\"Apple Ipad Gen 9th (2021) 10.2inch Wifi 64GB | Chp nh, quay video sc nt\" /></figure>\r\nThe rear camera Ipad Gen 9thth 2021 with 8MP resolution helps you record beautiful images and sharp, vivid videos, storing memorable moments in life. This iPad can also use the rear camera to scan documents or experience rich AR applications.\r\n<h2>iPadOS operating system, connecting accessories optimally</h2>\r\nIpad Gen 9thth 2021 is optimally designed for large screens with iPadOS operating system to help users find and organize information in the most efficient way. Users can split the screen to display two applications at the same time, bring widgets to the main screen or record moments anywhere.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/7/13/20220713_72d82e01-c1f6-4037-a211-1b40131978d0.jpg\" alt=\"Apple Ipad Gen 9th (2021) 10.2inch Wifi 64GB | H iu hnh iPadOS\" /></figure>\r\nThe iPad Gen 9th 2021 is compatible with useful accessories such as the Apple Pencil and Smart Keyboard. With a stylus, users can experience writing and drawing as natural as on paper to take notes or sketch works of art, edit and share quickly. As for the smart keyboard, it is an acc