i c<strong>iPhone</strong>, cc bn hon ton c th s dng chic bn phm ny  tng cng hiu qu g phm mt cch n tng. Khi s dng kt ni khng dy,<strong>APPLE Magic Keyboard</strong>khong cch ti a c cng b m cc bn c th s dng chic bn phm ny ln ti<strong>33 feet</strong>( ~10 mt ), mt khong cch cc k thoi mi  s dng ng khng cc bn?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Thi lng pin s dng vt tri</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>APPLE Magic Keyboard</strong>chuyn i t vic s dng pin thay th thnh<strong>pin sc</strong>, mt nc i cc k khn kho t Apple gip hon thin ti a tri nghim s dng cho ngi dng. Ch vi mt ln sc pin ko di<strong>2 ting ng h</strong>,<strong>APPLE Magic Keyboard</strong> sn sng  cc bn c th s dng trong<strong>mt thng</strong>v<strong>thm ch c th ko di hn</strong>.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\ni km theo hp sn phm, Apple  gi km theo chic bn phm ca chng ta mt si cp<strong>USB-C to Lightning</strong>. Khi s dng ht pin, vic n gin cc bn ch cn cm dy kt ni t chic bn phm ti cng USB-C trn MAC  c th va sc va dng mt cch tin dng. Tm bit cnh ang dng yn lnh m chic bn phm chng may ht pin  ri chng ta li phi mt cng i mua ri thay mi cc k bt tin.', 'Bn phm Apple Magic Keyboard (MK2A3ZA/A) (Silver)', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bn phm Magic mang li tri nghim nh my cc k thoi mi v chnh xc</li>\r\n 	<li>Bn phm khng dy v c th sc li</li>\r\n 	<li>Pin bn trong lu di s cung cp nng lng cho bn phm ca bn trong khong mt thng hoc hn gia cc ln sc</li>\r\n 	<li>T ng ghp ni vi my Mac ca bn, v vy bn c th bt u lm vic ngay lp tc</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ban-phim-apple-magic-keyboard-mk2a3za-a-silver', '', '', '2023-05-27 07:31:19', '2023-05-27 14:31:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=339', 0, 'product', '', 0),
