(345, 1, '2023-05-27 07:34:37', '2023-05-27 14:34:37', '<strong>Bn phm APPLE Magic Keyboard (MK2A3ZA/A)</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-main.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\nYou often have to edit documents and are having trouble using the virtual keyboard on Apple devices such as iPad, iMac, iPhone... If so, the perfect answer you are looking for The main sword is the APPLE Magic Keyboard. Possessing an extremely high level of perfection, luxurious appearance, sophisticated design and excellent performance, products from Apple have never disappointed us with the value that \"the home\" Apple always delivers and that is no exception on the APPLE Magic Keyboard.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLuxury, sophistication, minimalism and light\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\nThe keyboardAPPLE Magic Keyboardbrings users the most quintessential and core values of an Apple product. The outer shell (case) is made of high-grade aluminum, giving the keyboard an elegant and luxurious appearance but still comes with impressive durability and good impact resistance. And that\'s why, the keyboard has an extremely light weight of only 239 grams, which is convenient for you to carry anywhere without feeling even a little uncomfortable.\r\n\r\nAPPLE Magic Keyboarduses a high-end keycap set with white tonemainly with a large key surface area. The Font section is also extremely familiar when you can easily realize the complete synchronization between the Font of APPLE Magic Keyboard with the Font displayed on almost all devices of the Apple ecosystem. Each keycap is made extremely meticulously and perfectly so that we cannot recognize even the smallest mistake. All combined and properly represent the quality of a product in the high-end segment.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPractical, noise-canceling and impressive using experience\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\nWith the current trend, a wireless keyboardshould have a compact design for convenient carrying and use every day. And that \"trending\" was immediately applied by Apple to its beloved keyboard. APPLE Magic Keyboardis designed without the extra number pad to help bring the compact size of the keyboard. But, not so that the keyboard will lack useful functions. With the use of the Fn+ key combination, you can increase or decrease the screen brightness, volume, Multipedia cluster extremely comfortable and convenient enough to make you feel extremely satisfied with what you see. This super-luxury wireless keyboard delivers.\r\n\r\nWhen I tried the APPLE Magic Keyboard, I was really impressed by this wireless keyboard. Each key press feels extremely uniform when used, along with a good key bounce, giving an impressive feedback feeling completely different from conventional keyboards. APPLE Magic Keyboardis equipped with extremely good noise-canceling technology, so that you can comfortably use it in spaces that need quiet such as offices, lecture halls, libraries or cafes for you to relax and solve work. job.\r\n\r\nAPPLE Magic Keyboardhas a large key surface area, minimizing the phenomenon of mistakenly pressing during use. The keyboard is designed by Apple with a slight slope with a height of two sides top - bottom of 0.41 - 1.09 cm, respectively, helping us to have the most natural hand position, greatly reducing the phenomenon of fatigue. for long time use. The keyboard layout is made extremely familiar, bringing a sense of closeness right from the moment you buy it, rest assured to use it right away without spending time getting used to it like when buying other keyboards.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Wireless connection, automatic quick connection to Apple devices</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\nBecause it belongs to the Apple ecosystem, the Magic Keyboard is designed to be perfectly compatible with all devices that Apple brings. From Macbook, iPad to even iPhone, you can completely use this keyboard to enhance typing efficiency in an impressive way. When using a wireless connection, APPLE Magic Keyboard the published maximum distance that you can use this keyboard is up to 33 feet ( ~10 meters ), an extremely comfortable distance for proper use don\'t you guys?\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Outstanding battery life</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>APPLE Magic Keyboard</strong> switching from using a replacement battery to a rechargeable battery, an extremely clever move from Apple to maximize the user experience. With just a single battery charge that lasts2 hours,APPLE Magic Keyboardis ready for you to use fora monthandmaybe even longer.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://anphat.com.vn/media/lib/29-11-2021/kekh0026-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\nIncluded with the product box, Apple has included with our keyboard a USB-C to Lightning cable. When the battery runs out, simply plug in the connection cord from the keyboard to the USB-C port on the MAC to be able to charge and use it conveniently. Farewell to the scene of peaceful use but the keyboard unfortunately ran out of battery so that we had to waste time buying and replacing it, which was extremely inconvenient.', 'Keyboard Apple Magic Keyboard (MK2A3ZA/A) (Silver)', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Magic Keyboard provides an extremely comfortable and accurate typing experience</li>\r\n 	<li>Wireless and rechargeable keyboard</li>\r\n 	<li>The long-lasting internal battery will power your keyboard for about a month or more between charges</li>\r\n 	<li>Automatically pairs with your Mac, so you can start working right away</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'keyboard-apple-magic-keyboard-mk2a3za-a-silver', '', '', '2023-05-27 07:38:09', '2023-05-27 14:38:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=345', 0, 'product', '', 0),
