(347, 1, '2023-05-27 07:45:59', '2023-05-27 14:45:59', '<h2><a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/iphone-scat.01-N004-01\">iPhone</a>14 Plus thuc dng sn phm cao cp n t thng hiu ni ting Apple, chic in thoi ny c ra mt vo thng 9 nm 2022. Thot nhn<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/iphone-14-plus--p459614\">iPhone 14 Plus</a>c thit k ging iPhone 13, vi kch thc 6.7 inch mang n cm gic nhn thoi mi cng hiu nng mnh m ca chip A15 Bionic ha hn s p ng tt nhu cu s dng ca nhiu khch hng hin nay.</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_262379e9-acfc-451d-8a2d-8b77d5d53c2f.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus \" /></figure>\r\n<h3>Ngoi hnh sang trng c hon thin t cht liu cao cp, a dng phin bn mu sc</h3>\r\nin thoi di ng iPhone 14 Plus c v ngoi p mt nh c hon thin t<strong>cht liu cao cp</strong>vi mt lng knh sang trng gip tng thm tnh thm m cng  bn b n tng. 14 Plus s hu kch thc<strong>160.8 x 78.1 x 7.80mm</strong>cng khi lng<strong>203g</strong>cho cm gic chc chn khi cm trn tay.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_98a9be79-cc01-4570-a856-ece14ab02db1.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Thit k\" /></figure>\r\nNu bn mun s hu dng my c thit k, hiu nng tng t nhng c kch thc nh gn hn th hy tham kho qua phin bn<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/iphone-14--p459613\"><strong>iPhone 14</strong></a>thng hin ang c m bn sm ti Phong V.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_535e920d-6773-4e0f-9789-9c5d213dda59.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | a dng phin bn\" /></figure>\r\niPhone Plus mang n cho khch hng nhiu chn la mu sc ph hp vi tng s thch nh<strong>Blue, Midnight, Purple, Red, Starlight.</strong>Vi tng mu sc khc nhau s gip th hin c nhng nt c tnh ring cng nh vic gip cho bn la chn c nhng mu sc ng  cho bn thn.\r\n<h3>Tm nn Super Retina XDR OLED vi nhiu cng ngh hin i, kch thc mn hnh ln 6.7 inch</h3>\r\nin thoi iPhone 14 Plus trang b mn hnh<strong>Super Retina XDR OLED</strong>mang n nhiu tnh nng ni bt. Vi mn hnh ny gip ci thin  tng phn mu sc tt hn cng di mu chn thc gip em n tri nghim hnh nh t nhin hn, bn cnh  cn h tr cng ngh HDR10 v Dolby Vision gip nng tm tri nghim ca ngi dng khi gii tr chuyn nghip.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_c2adc111-84ef-413c-ae4f-9d38fd0c60c2.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Mn hnh\" /></figure>\r\nin thoi di ng iPhone 14 Plus s hu kch thc mn hnh kh ln ln n<strong>6.7 inch</strong>vi  phn gii t chun<strong>1284 x 2778pixels</strong>gip mang n tri nghim khc bit so vi phin bn iPhone 13 Series. 14 Plus mang n gii php mn hnh ln nhng gi thnh phi chng, y chnh l im khc bit gip dng Plus ny tr nn ni bt hn ht.\r\n<h3>a nhim mt m vi b nh RAM 6GB, nhiu s la chn v dung lng b nh trong</h3>\r\nin thoi iPhone 14 Plus c nng cp v kh nng a nhim khi c trang b b nh<strong>RAM 6GB,</strong>ln hn so vi phin bn iPhone 13 tin nhim. Nh , khch hng c th yn tm v kh nng a nhim ca th h iPhone mi ny, ha hn s em n cho khch hng nhng tri nghim tuyt vi nht.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_48252925-0890-4b6e-ab1c-6fe3ae409bbc.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Ram, b nh\" /></figure>\r\nin thoi di ng iPhone 14 Plus cho php ngi dng la chn khng gian lu tr ph hp vi tng nhu cu ca mi ngi bao gm cc mc dung lng quen thuc<strong>128GB</strong>,<strong>256GB</strong>v<strong>512GB.</strong>Khch hng c th la chn c dung lng lu tr ph hp cho nhu cu s dng ca mnh ty thch.\r\n<h3>Hiu nng cc khng n t con chip Apple A15 Bionic tn tin, h tr a dng chun kt ni hin i</h3>\r\nin thoi iPhone 14 Plus c nh Apple trang b chip<strong>Apple A15 Bionic</strong>vi hiu nng cc khng, y c xem l mt trong nhng dng chip x l trn in thoi di ng hng u th gii. Vi A15 Bionic cho hiu sut  ha c nng cao ng kinh ngc so vi dng chip trc , mang n tri nghim gii tr nng cao mt cch mt m cng kh nng ti u n tng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_8d7b446c-42f6-41b2-9b4f-2679b75aab2b.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Chip\" /></figure>\r\nBn cnh , in thoi di ng iPhone 14 Plus h tr a dng cc chun kt ni vi s h tr ca<strong>Nano-SIM</strong>v<strong>eSIM</strong>tin li. Khng nhng th, 14 Plus cn c h tr<strong>Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac/6, dual-band, hotspot</strong>mang n  n nh khi truy cp internet, cng<strong>Bluetooth 5.3</strong>cho kh nng kt ni khng dy n nh.\r\n<h3>H thng camera cho cht lng hnh nh sc nt, trang b pin lin Li-Ion h tr cng ngh sc tin li</h3>\r\nin thoi iPhone 14 Plus c nh sn xut trang b h thng camera kp<strong>12MP</strong>c t xo nhau ging nh phin bn iPhone 13 v iPhone 14 cng s kt hp ca b cm bin gip nng cao cht lng khi quay video. Tnh nng<strong>AutoFocus</strong>cng khu <strong>f/1.5</strong>gip ng knh thu c nhiu nh sng hn khi chp, song song vi  l kh nng chp gc rng kh n tng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_4ae27437-e402-455a-913a-75fb5794bf6e.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Camera\" /></figure>\r\nin thoi iPhone 14 Plus s dng vin pin<strong>Li-Ion</strong>cho thi lng pin c ci thin hn so vi phin bn iPhone 13 trc  gip em n kh nng p ng nhu cu vi cc tc v c bn. Khng nhng th, 14 Plus cn h tr cng ngh sc nhanh khng dy<strong>Magsafe</strong>ln n<strong>15W</strong>cng vi sc khng dy<strong>chun Qi</strong>ln n<strong>7.5W</strong>cho kh nng sc y pin mt cch nhanh chng.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_1652ab28-2d7b-40b8-a585-e1f930011ced.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Pin\" /></figure>', 'iPhone 14 Plus | Chnh hng VNA', '- Chnh hng, Mi 100%, Nguyn seal\r\n- Mn hnh: Super Retina XDR OLED\r\n- Camera sau: 2 x 12MP\r\n- Camera trc: 12MP\r\n- CPU: Apple A15 Bionic\r\n- B nh: 1