(385, 1, '2023-05-27 07:56:21', '2023-05-27 14:56:21', '<h2>iPhone 14 Plus belongs to the high-end product line from the famous brand Apple, this phone was launched in September 2022. At first glance, the iPhone 14 Plus has the same design as the iPhone 13, with a size of 6.7 inches that brings a sense of touch. The comfortable look and strong performance of the A15 Bionic chip promises to meet the needs of many customers today.</h2>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_262379e9-acfc-451d-8a2d-8b77d5d53c2f.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus \" /></figure>\n<h3>Luxurious appearance is completed from high-quality materials, a variety of color versions</h3>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus mobile phone has a beautiful appearance thanks to its finishing ofpremium materialswith a luxurious glass back that enhances its aesthetics and impressive durability. 14 Plus has dimensions 160.8 x 78.1 x 7.80mmwith a weight of 203gfor a solid feel in the hand.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_98a9be79-cc01-4570-a856-ece14ab02db1.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Thit k\" /></figure>\nIf you want to own a model with similar design and performance but with a more compact size, please refer to the regular version of iPhone 14, which is currently on sale soon in Phong Vu.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_535e920d-6773-4e0f-9789-9c5d213dda59.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | a dng phin bn\" /></figure>\niPhone Plus gives customers a variety of color options to suit each taste such as Blue, Midnight, Purple, Red, Starlight. With different colors will help express your own personality as well as help you choose the right color for yourself.\n<h3>Super Retina XDR OLED panel with many modern technologies, large screen size of 6.7 inches</h3>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus is equipped with aSuper Retina XDR OLEDscreen that offers many outstanding features. With this screen, it helps to improve color contrast better and true color range for a more natural visual experience, besides it also supports HDR10 and Dolby Vision technology to enhance the user experience. professional entertainment.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_c2adc111-84ef-413c-ae4f-9d38fd0c60c2.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Mn hnh\" /></figure>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus mobile phone has a rather large screen size of up to 6.7 incheswith a standard resolution of 1284 x 2778pixelswhich helps to bring a different experience compared to the iPhone 13 Series version. 14 Plus offers a large screen solution at an affordable price, which is the difference that makes this Plus series stand out.\n<h3>Smooth multitasking with 6GB RAM, multiple choices of internal memory</h3>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus is upgraded in terms of multitasking when equipped with 6GB of RAM, which is larger than its predecessor iPhone 13. As a result, customers can be assured of the multitasking ability of this new generation of iPhones, promising to bring customers the best experience.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_48252925-0890-4b6e-ab1c-6fe3ae409bbc.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Ram, b nh\" /></figure>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus mobile phone allows users to choose the right storage space for each person\'s needs including the familiar 128GB, 256GBand 512GB. Customers can choose the right amount of storage for their needs.\n<h3>Extreme performance comes from the advanced Apple A15 Bionic chip, supporting a variety of modern connection standards</h3>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus is equipped with the Apple A15 Bionic chip with tremendous performance, which is considered one of the world\'s leading mobile phone processor lines. With the A15 Bionic, the graphics performance is amazingly enhanced compared to the previous chip series, providing a smooth enhanced entertainment experience with impressive optimization capabilities.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_8d7b446c-42f6-41b2-9b4f-2679b75aab2b.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Chip\" /></figure>\nBesides, the iPhone 14 Plus mobile phone supports a variety of connection standards with the convenient Nano-SIM and eSIM support. Not only that, the 14 Plus also supports Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac/6, dual-band, hotspotfor stable internet access, and Bluetooth 5.3for wireless connectivity. stable wire.\n<h3>Camera system for sharp image quality, equipped with Li-Ion battery that supports convenient charging technology</h3>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus phone is equipped with a dual camera system 12MP, placed diagonally like the iPhone 13 and iPhone 14 versions, with a combination of sensors to improve the quality when recording videos. The AutoFocusand aperture f/1.5helps the lens capture more light when shooting, along with its impressive wide-angle shooting ability.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_4ae27437-e402-455a-913a-75fb5794bf6e.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Camera\" /></figure>\nThe iPhone 14 Plus uses a Li-Ion battery for improved battery life compared to the previous iPhone 13 version, helping to provide the ability to meet the needs of basic tasks. Not only that, the 14 Plus also supports fast wireless charging technologyMagsafeup to 15Wwith wireless chargingQi standardup to 7.5Wfor the ability to quickly fully charge the battery.\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/21/20220921_1652ab28-2d7b-40b8-a585-e1f930011ced.png\" alt=\"iPhone 14 Plus | Pin\" /></figure>', 'iPhone 14 Plus | Genuine VNA', '- Genuine, New 100%, Original seal\n- Screen: Super Retina XDR OLED\n- Rear camera: 2 x 12MP\n- Front camera: 12MP\n- CPU: Apple A15 Bionic\n- Memory: 128GB\n- RAM: 6GB\n- Operating system: IOS', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '369-autosave-v1', '', '', '2023-05-27 07:56:21', '2023-05-27 14:56:21', '', 369, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?p=385', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
