(403, 1, '2023-05-27 08:15:12', '2023-05-27 15:15:12', '<h2>Product Review:Soundmax A130 Speaker (2.0) (Green)</h2>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-16655 size-full\" src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Loa-Soundmax-A130-2.0-Xanh-1-e1540141297880.png\" alt=\"Loa Soundmax A130 (2.0) (Xanh)\" width=\"1000\" height=\"760\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSpeakerSoundmax A-130is a mini speaker with a compact, dynamic design. Power of each speaker 3W and frequency range from 50Hz - 20KHz for loud and clear sound. Simple to use, including a 3.5mm audio jack and a USB power cord to connect to the USB port of a laptop or desktop for use.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"featureContent_title\">Compact design</h3>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-16658 size-full\" src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Loa-Soundmax-A130-2.0-Xanh-3-e1540142323642.jpg\" alt=\"Loa Soundmax A130 (2.0) (Xanh)\" width=\"591\" height=\"349\" /><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-16659 size-full\" src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Loa-Soundmax-A130-2.0-Xanh-2-e1540143213961.png\" alt=\"Loa Soundmax A130 (2.0) (Xanh)\" width=\"795\" height=\"610\" />\r\n\r\nThe compact Soundmax A130 computer speaker consists of two box-shaped speakers with many colors, curves at a beautifully stylized corner. Volume control button integrated right on the power cordcan be adjusted quickly.\r\n\r\nThe black plastic cover, red or blue border around it attracts users, the speaker face is facing up to help the sound spread evenly.\r\n\r\nThe plastic speaker cover helps you use the speaker for a long time without worrying about heat conduction.\r\n<h3>Real sound</h3>\r\n2.0 speaker system, for clear, clear sound to hear a variety of music. Bring clear, honest sound quality to a space with a moderate area, without causing interference or noise to affect people around.\r\n<h3 class=\"featureContent_title\">Quality speaker system</h3>\r\nWith a speaker system with a capacity of 6W, with a frequency response of 50-20kHz, Soundmax computer speakers produce the most realistic, vivid and quality sound.\r\n<h3 class=\"featureContent_title\">Jack 3.5 mm</h3>\r\nThe 3.5mm jack oncomputer speakersmakes you enjoy your music with the devices you have with excellent sound quality.\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"NkPdp_productFeature\">\r\n<div class=\"productFeature_content\">\r\n<div class=\"featureContent featureContent_2col feature_img-txt\">\r\n<div class=\"featureContent_col-2\">\r\n<div class=\"featureContent_col_wrap\">\r\n<h3 class=\"featureContent_title\">USB connection</h3>\r\nSoundmax A130 computer speaker is easy to carry on the go, USB connection draws power from devices with USB connectors.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Speaker 2.0 Soundmax A130 (Blue, Black)', '-  2.0 speaker system, for clear, clear sound to hear a variety of music.\r\n- Use for all kinds of computers such as: desktop (PC), Laptop (Laptop)...\r\n- Compact size, suitable for carrying or moving when needed.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'speaker-2-0-soundmax-a130-blue-black', '', '', '2023-05-27 08:15:13', '2023-05-27 15:15:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=403', 0, 'product', '', 0),
