(412, 1, '2023-05-27 08:22:11', '2023-05-27 15:22:11', '<h2>ReviewHeadphoneSoundmax AH 304 - Give users an immersive sound experience at an affordable price.</h2>\r\nThe SoundMax AH 304 headset is designed in the form of an earcup with 2 large ear buds, embracing the user\'s ears to make the gaming and music listening experience more distinctive and vivid. With a compact design and 2 ear buds on the inside are designed with soft cushions, so users can use it comfortably without causing ear pain.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Tai-nghe-Soundmax-AH-304_2.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Soundmax AH 304 | thoi mi m khng gy au tai\" /></figure>\r\nSoundMax AH 304 headphones have the outer surface of 2 ear cups made of high-quality impact-resistant plastic, ensuring the safety of the headset, the dome is made of sturdy metal and covered with elastic plastic material. High rebound fits users with small and large head sizes.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Tai-nghe-Soundmax-AH-304_3.jpg\" alt=\"Tai nghe Soundmax AH 304 | vm chp u c lm kim loi\" /></figure>\r\nSoundMax AH 304 headset is also equipped with a microphone that can be rotated, folded, bent and the ability to accurately transmit sound right on the left earbud so that users can use it for software and games that support Voice. ChatlikeDiscord, Facebook, Garena, PUBG, CSGO,....Along with it, the Headset is also designed with a volume control panel on the cord in a convenient position to help users easily customize volume at will in an easy, comfortable way.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://tmp.phongvu.vn/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Tai-nghe-Soundmax-AH-304_1.png\" alt=\"Tai nghe Soundmax AH 304 | microphone c th xoay, gp\" /></figure>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSoundMax AH 304 headphones use a USB connection standard with a length of 2m and are covered with flexible PVC material, which can certainly be wrapped and