(422, 1, '2023-05-27 08:35:28', '2023-05-27 15:35:28', 'The Logitech H390 headset is capable of producing high-end digital sound, the receiver mic has very good noise filtering capabilities. This type of headset is often used by business people to work on computers. In particular, in meetings, this is the type of headset that is used a lot to transmit sound.\r\n\r\n<strong>Transparent sound, popular in-line controls</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Logitech H390 headset allows users to experience common internet calls with crystal-clear sound, USB-A connectivity, and a noise-cancelling mic. The headphones\' diaphragms are adjustable for high-end engineering sound.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2021/4/17/20210417_132111fb-6a06-4489-8e74-7eb2300427bf.png\" /></figure>\r\nThe Logitech H390 headset has in-line controls to help users comfortably control the listening volume, mute but without interrupting the call. In addition, the headset also has the ability to adjust the laser to create the best sound.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2021/4/17/20210417_460ba893-50a5-4a8b-ab67-57b67f77d1ef.png\" /></figure>\r\n<strong>USB-A connection, noise canceling microphone</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Logitech H390 headset has USB-capable drivers, so it\'s easy to connect and operate. Users only need to plug the USB connector into the computer to be able to talk, listen to music and play games.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2021/4/17/20210417_7ca85889-9a92-49fa-9670-5fcdce611d3e.png\" /></figure>\r\nThe Logitech H390 headset has the ability to reduce unwanted background noise during calls. Users can reduce the noise by adjusting the mic on the left to put it in a position to get better sound.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2021/4/17/20210417_7bad9b8c-fdec-4cff-a8b8-974d4f53750f.png\" /></figure>\r\n<strong>Comfortable to use, easy to clean</strong>\r\n\r\nThe padded headband and earcups of the Logitech H390 headset have soft, faux-leather wedges. So you can use it for hours without any discomfort.\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2021/4/17/20210417_b7e2e4aa-ccb4-4d64-8055-30e209195f5b.png\" /></figure>\r\nThe Logitech H390 headset has pads made of imitation leather, so it is easy to clean and clean. You just need to take a wet cloth to gently wipe the surface of the headset to remove all dirt.', 'Logitech H390 . Headset', '- Just plug in the USB-A port and it\'s ready to use\r\n- In-line controls allow volume control without interrupting calls\r\n- Padded leatherette shoulder straps and earcups are comfortable to wear for hours\r\n- Noise-cancelling microphone reduces background noise when talking', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'logitech-h390-headset', '', '', '2023-05-27 08:35:29', '2023-05-27 15:35:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/UDNM/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=422', 0, 'product', '', 0),
